00:33:09.730 --> 00:33:12.370
If you are a good C++ developer

00:33:12.450 --> 00:33:16.010
who develops a control system for an airplane,

00:33:16.010 --> 00:33:19.000
it does not mean you're a good pilot.

00:33:19.000 --> 00:33:20.600
If you really think you are,

00:33:20.600 --> 00:33:24.240
let me know which flight you're piloting,

00:33:24.240 --> 00:33:26.750
I will take another flight.

00:33:26.750 --> 00:33:29.990
So it is really a profession.

00:33:29.990 --> 00:33:33.470
And just like automation is also a profession,

00:33:33.470 --> 00:33:36.350
a good programmer is not necessarily

00:33:36.350 --> 00:33:38.150
a good automation engineer.

00:33:38.230 --> 00:33:42.990
It has, automation is a very specific craft.

00:33:42.990 --> 00:33:47.070
You have to deal with timing and identification of objects

00:33:47.070 --> 00:33:48.990
