00:34:22.460 --> 00:34:24.980
Automation is not a question mark.

00:34:24.980 --> 00:34:27.460
Everything is done with automation

00:34:27.460 --> 00:34:29.860
because in DevOps you're essentially

00:34:29.860 --> 00:34:33.780
automating the entire integration and deployment process,

00:34:33.780 --> 00:34:36.660
including provisioning test machines

00:34:36.660 --> 00:34:38.060
and running tests on them.

00:34:38.060 --> 00:34:41.660
So automation is not really a question anymore.

00:34:43.220 --> 00:34:46.100
