00:35:33.830 --> 00:35:36.590
Ops is also a craft, obligations.

00:35:36.590 --> 00:35:40.190
Planning, production, planning, testing,

00:35:40.190 --> 00:35:43.470
planning environments, which can be very different

00:35:43.470 --> 00:35:47.390
for different companies, for different organizations,

00:35:48.230 --> 00:35:49.790
what that actually means.

00:35:49.790 --> 00:35:52.390
But it is a craft.

00:35:52.390 --> 00:35:54.510
It is a different way of thinking

00:35:54.510 --> 00:35:59.510
than making if statements in a function.

00:35:59.670 --> 00:36:03.670
That is, it's all craft.

00:36:03.670 --> 00:36:07.360
And one of the very positive things

00:36:07.360 --> 00:36:10.600
that currently is happening is that you cooperate.

00:36:10.600 --> 00:36:13.720
So your foreign teams and those teams cooperate.

00:36:13.720 --> 00:36:17.200
That means that the developers, the business owners

00:36:17.200 --> 00:36:20.320
