00:36:20.320 --> 00:36:23.640
And you get the best test and the best results

00:36:23.640 --> 00:36:25.640
when you are in the same team.

00:36:25.640 --> 00:36:27.400
Because then you can talk to the developers

00:36:27.400 --> 00:36:30.120
