00:39:38.350 --> 00:39:41.830
and let them go through the B channel,

00:39:41.830 --> 00:39:45.750
you just let your automated test go for the B channel.

00:39:45.750 --> 00:39:47.390
And if it doesn't work,

00:39:47.390 --> 00:39:50.030
then you don't put that particular component

00:39:50.030 --> 00:39:51.710
